room_title: Escape room "Sheriff Roy" by Riddle Room in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description: That darn sheriff has sent his deputies to arrest you! But the problem is, they won’t tell you what you’ve done to be arrested. All you know is that you haven’t committed any crimes and that you’re pretty sure the proof of your innocence is somewhere in Sheriff Roy’s office. If only you can find it before his deputies return…
